{"title":"锡林郭勒大草原","authors":["白原"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":10,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"锡林郭勒大草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锡林郭勒大草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊连云草连天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马群汹涌如波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丘陵起伏渺无边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河落鸿雁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塞外春水寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百灵迎风飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月雪花卷满天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧民移场走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊车马喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勒勒车停靠蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古包外春草鲜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘煮奶茶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妈接羔忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿爸草场去放牧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社浩特绕炊烟。〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古青年驰骏马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"套马杆头云飘荡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锡林郭勒牧场上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛羊马群漫草原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜宿蒙古包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜宿蒙古包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶茶热气灯下绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古少女诺斯劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀抱羊羔灯前笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤主妇契林卓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙煮奶茶话接羔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母羊怀胎五个月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧民妇女真辛劳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月春来雪未消，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接羔季节说就到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小羔脱胎不等人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊群里头来回跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜提灯巡羊圈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明踏雪去认羔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀抱羔羊寻母羊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒风吹舞蒙古袍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原茫茫朝霞里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌儿伴送彩云飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原夜风嚎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地任飘摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古包里人声静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圈里睡满小羊羔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"守羊狗吠声阵阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月黑天里闻狼嗥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"契林卓，深夜起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圈里圈外摸又照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体财富情满怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整夜牵挂度春宵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜风阵阵响又停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤我醒来又睡着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原遍地是鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"芳草芊芊人不老。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦里醒来阳光照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羊群滚滚似海涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕在锡林郭勒草原，四、五个蒙古包分为一个浩特，由公社生产队领导，等于一个作业小组，以一个浩特为单位移场放牧。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}